title: Members of the Queensland Legislative Assembly, 1867–1868
content: This is a list of members of the 3rd Legislative Assembly of Queensland from 1867 to 1868, as elected at the 1867 colonial elections held between 18 June 1867 and 19 July 1867 (due to problems of distance and communications, it was not possible to hold the elections on a single day).[1]
concepts: Members of the Queensland Legislative Assembly, 1867–1868
